most_active_tickets.title: Pieces Pro: checkout is not opening

common_issues.title: Pieces Pro checkout not opening
common_issues.description: Users are unable to open the Pieces Pro checkout modal. The "Upgrade Now" button changes to "Awaiting checkout..." but nothing happens. This issue occurs on both the Desktop and Pieces OS app.  A possible solution is to check the browser or network connectivity.

recommendations: Investigate the issue preventing users from opening the Pieces Pro checkout modal. This appears to be affecting both Desktop and Pieces OS apps and is hindering Pro upgrades.
Check browser and network connectivity issues as a potential cause of the checkout problem.
Review the Pieces OS logs for error messages related to the checkout process.
Prioritize resolution of issue #825, "Pieces Pro: checkout is not opening," as it has the highest activity level and represents a potential revenue loss.
